- if 2 or 4, incentivising impact is flawed, decoupled from research quality
- research impact ``involves subtle, incremental and diffuse ideational adjustments over a long period of time, which are generated by a wide range of research insights rather than specific individual findings'', should reward collaborative endeavours},
